name: xBURGER Token
description: xBURGER is the token of BurgerShack of BurgerSwap.org, BurgerShack would charge 10% of the mining revenue for the repurchasing and burning of xBURGER and BURGER, of which 8% will be used to repurchase and burn xBURGER, and 2% will be used to repurchase and burn BURGER.
